An annoyance that goes away after a rebuild but on an initial build this seems
to be hge error message

<error>
 Unable to locate resource: cmsui (key [cmsui])

 org.apache.cocoon.ProcessingException: Unable to locate resource: cmsui
 (key [cmsui]): org.apache.avalon.framework.component.ComponentException:

cocoon-2.1.5, launched jetty and there was the error. Rebuild lenya and the
error was gone.
this is a fallback message and can be safely ignored, right roku?
